            <bug_when>2009-09-18 19:58:59 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>The migration script assumes that you are migrating from 0.7.x and may generate erroneous results if you accept the default, but in fact are at a later release already.

Migration should NOT assume the base version; AND

Documentation for migration should expressly state how to tell what version you are at BEFORE beginning the upgrade.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
